Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Original Translation by Triad / Softsub by Urusai


Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not believe me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even before he told me his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I felt as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I already knew who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... Motoharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:35.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:41.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:47.98,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:53.95,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:01:01.33,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:06.04,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:11.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:20.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:25.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:32.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:39.66,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:35.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:41.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:47.98,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:53.95,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:01:01.33,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:06.04,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:11.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:20.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:25.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:32.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:39.66,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.67,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takahashi Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my second day of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.42,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if I could make lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For now, I'll try to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... I'm Takahashi Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yamamoto Yuri. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm, what middle school are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... we have to change classrooms for home ec, right? Can I go with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you were in the first seat in the front, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm Takahashi Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What middle school are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,South.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both from West.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There don't seem to be any girls in our class from Asahi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this girl Yamamoto-san who sits next to me is from Asahi Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You talked to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've heard a lot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were with Motoharu during the winter session, and he's just so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was popular with both the girls and guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even say that in his last year of middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...two-thirds of the girls in class were in love with him at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So someone like that is in the same class as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hey, you're from the same middle school as Yano-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard two-thirds of the girls fell for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nana, wanna be on the class committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I prefer an easy life, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanna be with Motoharu on the committee...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the procedure for joining it? Do you get nominated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though announcing it by yourself is kinda lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I nominate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... what was her name again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu... Mizu something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly ask her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm, what was that girl's name again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu... Mizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not believe me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even before he told me his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... I felt as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... I already knew who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano Motoharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be the class president.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this nomination's a little arbitrary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody nominated anyone else or nominated themselves, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll nominate someone. I nominate myself as {\i1}vice{\i0} president.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, taking the easy way out again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice President Yano-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... umm, I'd also like to nominate someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the role of secretary, Mizuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you mean Mizuguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, I ended up as class president...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.88,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assign everyone's duties and decide the class goals, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty rude of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lied to me before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... was I more rude than forgetting someone's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is kind of annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it really my fault for forgetting her name...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if Yano-kun's had a girlfriend before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard he's gone out with a lot of different girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both younger and older!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. They're just rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try asking Yamamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I'm a part of the other third of the class...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me about him. I don't know. Not interested in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't as fun as I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, did you finish your career counseling session?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I didn't understand it very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.32,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I should've joined a club, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long did your career counseling session last?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it took half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it took only five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding, it took fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, bye by--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I thought you didn't hear me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye... bye bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! This isn't my heart beating faster for him... he only surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't think he'd call out to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I just don't understand Math I at all, and I was getting frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You plan on using math down you career path?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I plan to go to a liberal arts private school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why bother worrying about the sciences?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'd be wiser to use this time focusing on liberal arts instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... when you're so bad at something, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're bad at it, nothing will come from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't help you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why people do useless things they don't even like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I heard the week after next is a school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have tests before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'm gonna do. I haven't studied at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna be a piece of cake for you, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, I've practically given up. I'll probably get a zero or something in math.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A zero, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... I actually got a zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably decide who's in charge of the trip soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... the people to head the teams, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And about buying stuff for the trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah? About buying stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain, so can you go with the girls to take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sur- huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... umm...! I just wasn't feeling well, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.91,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you and the girls to take care of the shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why do we always get the annoying stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, amazing stuff! Takahashi's math grade was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.46,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go! We'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be tricked, don't be tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he smiled like that, it's just because he threatened to blurt out your math grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go on to the next grade with a failing mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yamamoto-san, didn't you say to drop math if I was aiming for liberal arts school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a failing grade is no good, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put this... there are times when you begin to hate everything around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's up with my heart thumping like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I wanted to look at the sky, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that zero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get the same...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I got an 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, do you really think it's worth worrying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Everyone is good at something. Isn't it all right if you just try your best at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, don't you think getting a zero's pretty impressive in another way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, is there anything you're not good at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to nothing, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too popular with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, do you have trouble with anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stand out, so I'm always being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though it's annoying, I normally get picked to be on the class committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hate... fickle girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes five! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... none of those are problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you say "fickle", do you really have the right to talk that way about others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my looks, I'm pretty single-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I seem that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of girls Yano falls for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of girls he's fallen for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.. if the girl you were going out with was fickle, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I want to know his answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why I asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, if you have any problems, I'll lend an ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... about anything. You just listened to me go on, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad. I don't have any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that smile again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this is happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely going to be the worst mistake of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... I like--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and about your problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a right reserved for the living, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment... I didn't know what Yano meant when he said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take note of these important points during our walkathon school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will travel by bus to the starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire length is 42 km, and... hey, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain this important stuff to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The use of cell phones is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no shopping at any shops along the path!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No using you cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I feel so pathetic, falling for someone incredibly irresponsible like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to collect everyone's cell phones now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he really not have one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that grin...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I forgot to bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yano really doesn't have one with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's so nice out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might actually be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be able to make it the whole 42 km...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:20.95,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I sure want to eat lunch with Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, talk to him for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have a relationship with him since you're prez and he's vice prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I guess I have no choice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Want to have lunch together, Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, inviting Yamamoto-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Yano, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My timing was off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to eat with Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that we don't want to, she's just hard to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gives off a dark aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just fine and all... but be sure to invite Yano and the others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, what am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I invite Yano now, it'll be like I did it to harass Yamamoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though almost nobody hates him, I wonder why Yamamoto-san does...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... who's that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they were both in same class in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, they still seem to hang out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the half way point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That went by fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you'll be able to walk the whole 42 km?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Want to eat lunch with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure, but... can you keep up with our pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm starting to get tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery isn't changing a bit, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get bored of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've retired at the 20 km mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... wanna sit down for lunch now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we lost track of Yano and the others, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the teachers will pass by in their cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I think they're eating lunch at the cabin back at the 20 km halfway point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be by in an hour or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An hour or two, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, if I find someone who can get in touch with them, I'll let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san, can you eat some fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might refresh you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some cold juice with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll get better if she takes a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we have to wait for the teachers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good... I'm the one who's supposed to be responsible, but I can't do anything to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Someone's heading back this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take got in touch with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got in touch with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Did you eat breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any symptoms of dehydration?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try licking some salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get someone with a car to come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how will we contact the teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's me. Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 25 km in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long before you reach the goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers haven't passed by yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:33.89,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... he kept it hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to return to the halfway point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The halfway point?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're eating lunch in the barbecue house at the lodge back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go now to get them, they can be back here in five minutes if they drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do any of you have your cell phones with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us... they were taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you girls keep control of your own cell phones?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have mine... so we'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. You stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm pretty much the responsible party here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you start slowing me down, I'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your number hasn't changed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know each other's cell phone numbers because they were in the same class in middle school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you walking like a snail? I'll seriously leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm such a bad person... worrying about something else when Yamamoto-san is like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, were you close to Yamamoto-san in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. She hardly talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been pretty quiet since a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's been like that since long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "like that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she doesn't really express her feelings... I wonder if she's a single child?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... huh? Past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. She died last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it better that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems like the type who would hate being pitied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... did you go to the funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was summer vacation, after all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've... never experienced anything like that, so I don't really understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be really difficult, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... really an unsympathetic girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're having this discussion, my heart's beating really fast because of Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she came down with a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 25 km point, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sensei, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. I haven't had any beer, so I should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, shouldn't we go with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more we can do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave the rest to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two plates of beef ribs and two Oolong teas, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say one should be efficient in life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... and some cow tongue and barbecued beef giblets too, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really helped that you were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen someone with as carefree a smile as his...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're late! What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san was taken home by the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it was just the common cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... buses will be leaving from all over, so please make sure you board the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we just parted from each other... I want to see him again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for before. It really helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how did things turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we got a teacher to come by in a car and take her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking you were all so great, thinking on behalf of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... a lot's happened, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you heard about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... if it were me, I wouldn't be able to get back up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one close to me has died yet, so I don't really get it, but I wonder how it must feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if a person would just put a stopper on their life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I feel like they're a different type of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but you can't just tell from their outward appearance, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, really... it's kind of bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen them cry before... and I think it'd be better if they'd just cry or let it distract them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no idea if they're over it, or if they're still saddened about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or something else entirely... I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to talk about them like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying they're "scary". I think they're really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's okay not to keep it all bottled up sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be really frustrating because you're friends, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun, you're really that close...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Even though we're in different classes, we're still friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sunburnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to peel it all off...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice face you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that something you normally say to a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about "that's quite a face".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so shameless, stuck-up, irresponsible, and impossible to deal with, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him a whole lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san's older sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You big liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was... Yano's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:39.08,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Taisetsu na anata no hitomi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:44.96,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi wa utsutteru no ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:57.60,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimorehi zashikomu madobe ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:05.11,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite yasashiku narerun darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:11.91,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro kakushite kodou kakushite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.16,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:20.54,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakariaenai tsurasa ga tamaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:29.80,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Waraitai waraitai kokoro no mannaka de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:34.31,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ni wa uchiakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:39.06,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaru watashi yowaki na watashi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:41.31,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinou no hanashi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:44.57,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,dou demo ii koto mo zenbu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:49.40,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Aishiteru kore kara mo zuttoo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:55.70,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ude wo kunde aruite ikou YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:11.34,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu wa watashi dake nokoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:18.10,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Taisetsu na hito tsurete yukun da ne
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:25.73,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wo sagashite kimi wo sagashite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.73,0:24:31.99,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna toki demo kimi wo sagashiteiru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.99,0:24:37.24,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsukaru no sore wa kimi na no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:43.58,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanashikute kanashikute
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:48.25,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,nakidashisou ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.25,0:24:56.85,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dore dake no omoi nara dakishimete kureru no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.85,0:25:02.14,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah waraitai waraitai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:06.73,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Nani mo ka mo nagesutete
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.73,0:25:11.15,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ni wa uchiakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.15,0:25:15.95,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinou no hanashi ashita no hanashi
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.95,0:25:21.58,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari no mirai kakaekirenai hodo zenbu
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:26.25,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakusoku wa shinakutemo ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:32.63,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari massugu ni arukou YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:39.08,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm reflected
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:44.96,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,in your precious eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:57.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how I can always be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:05.11,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,on the windowsill where the sunshine always falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:11.91,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I hide my true feelings and the thumping of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.16,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As always,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:20.54,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the pain of being able to understand each other burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:29.80,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smile, I want to smile, down to the core of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:34.31,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:39.06,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about how I pretend to be strong, about how I'm weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:41.31,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about what happened yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:44.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,about everything that means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:49.40,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue to love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:55.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my arm and let's walk. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:11.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The seasons leave only me behind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:18.10,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and take my precious person away, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:25.73,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I look for you, I look for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.73,0:24:31.99,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.99,0:24:33.99,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I find that person, is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:43.58,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sad, I'm so sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:48.25,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I could cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.25,0:24:56.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,How much feeling must I give to be able to embrace you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.85,0:25:02.14,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I want to smile, I want to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:06.73,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing everything away,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.73,0:25:11.15,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.15,0:25:15.95,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,About yesterday, about tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.95,0:25:21.58,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,about our future and everything, so much that I can't even take it all myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:26.25,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to promise me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:32.63,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just keep walking. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.90,0:25:06.74,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.70,0:25:09.74,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:11.12,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, wanna go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.12,0:25:13.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You really like me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.20,0:25:15.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.20,0:25:17.42,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that sort of "like"...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.42,0:25:19.79,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you\N really, really like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.79,0:25:21.59,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.59,0:25:23.38,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.38,0:25:25.76,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,My girlfriend was a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.76,0:25:28.38,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,She was with \Nanother guy when she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.38,0:25:30.01,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It was her previous boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.01,0:25:32.43,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,They were never\N through with one another...
